org.springframework.beans
Interface PropertyValues

All Known Implementing Classes:
MutablePropertyValues, PortletRequestParameterPropertyValues, ServletRequestParameterPropertyValues
public interface PropertyValues

Holder containing one or more PropertyValue objects, typically comprising one update for a specific target bean.

Since:
13 May 2001
Author:
Rod Johnson, Juergen Hoeller
See Also:
